'''Tom<U+00E1>s Barris''' (born 1 February 1930) is a [[Spain|Spanish]] former [[Middle distance running|middle distance runner]] who competed in the [[1960 Summer Olympics]].<ref name=sref>{{cite web|title=Olympics |url=http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ba/tomas-barris-1.html|publisher=sports-reference|accessdate=14 May 2012}}</ref>

